18  import org.gradoop.temporal.model.impl.operators.matching.TemporalTestData;
19  
20  import java.util.ArrayList;
21  import java.util.Collection;
22  
23  public class HomomorphismMinMaxTest implements TemporalTestData {
24  
25    @Override
26    public Collection<String[]> getData() {
27      ArrayList<String[]> data = new ArrayList<>();
28  
29      // 1. [ (9 Ave & W 18)<-[e0]-(Broadway & W24)-[e1]-> (9 Ave & W  18)]
30      // 2. [ (9 Ave & W 18)<-[e1]-(Broadway & W24)-[e0]-> (9 Ave & W  18)]
31      data.add(new String[] {
32        "MinMax_HOM_1_default_citibike",
33        "MATCH (a)<-[e1]-(b)-[e2]->(c) " +
34          "WHERE e1.tx_from!=e2.tx_from AND MIN(a.tx_from, b.tx_from, c.tx_from)=Timestamp(2013-05-10)",
35        "expected1,expected2",
36        "expected1[(s1)<-[e0]-(s0)-[e1]->(s1)],expected2[(s1)<-[e1]-(s0)-[e0]->(s1)]"
37      });
38  
39      // 1. [ (9 Ave & W 18)<-[e0]-(Broadway & W24)-[e1]-> (9 Ave & W  18)]
40      // 2. [ (9 Ave & W 18)<-[e1]-(Broadway & W24)-[e0]-> (9 Ave & W  18)]
41      data.add(new String[] {
42        "MinMax_HOM_2_default_citibike",
43        "MATCH (a)<-[e1]-(b)-[e2]->(c) " +
44          "WHERE e1.tx_from!=e2.tx_from AND MAX(a.tx_to, b.tx_to, c.tx_to)=Timestamp(2013-07-18)",
45        "expected1,expected2",
46        "expected1[(s1)<-[e0]-(s0)-[e1]->(s1)],expected2[(s1)<-[e1]-(s0)-[e0]->(s1)]"
47      });
48  
49      // empty
50      data.add(new String[] {
51        "MinMax_HOM_3_default_citibike",
52        "MATCH (a)-[e]->(b) WHERE val_from!=MAX(a.val_from,e.val_from) OR " +
53          "val_to!=MIN(b.val_to,e.val_to)",
54        "[]",
55        "[]"
56      });
57  
58      // empty
59      data.add(new String[] {
60        "MinMax_HOM_4_default_citibike",
61        "MATCH (a)-[e]->(b) WHERE NOT a.tx.join(b.tx).equals(" +
62          "Interval(MIN(a.tx_from, b.tx_from), MAX(a.tx_to, b.tx_to)))",
63        "[]",
64        "[]"
65      });
66  
67      return data;
68    }
